# Omni Brain

## 📌 Overview
Omni Brain is an AI-powered intelligent assistant designed to understand natural language, answer user queries, and perform various tasks using a Large Language Model (LLM). The project provides a user-friendly interface where users can interact with the AI in real time.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🤖 AI-powered conversational assistant
- 💬 Natural language understanding
- ⚡ Fast and intelligent responses
- 🔍 Information retrieval
- 📚 Context-aware conversations
- 🔒 Secure and scalable architecture
- 🌐 Easy-to-use web interface

---

